Title: Quantum Mechanics and Thermodynamics of Particles with Distance

Dependent StatisticsAuthors: Stefan V.Mashkevich

Comments: 9 pages, LATEX Kiev Institute for Theoretical Physics preprint

ITP-93-5E, January 1993Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D48 (1993) 5953-5956

The general notion of distance dependent statistics in anyon-like systems isdiscussed. The two-body problem for such statistics is considered, the generalformula for the second virial coefficient is derived and it is shown that inthe limiting cases it reproduces the known results for ideal anyons.